item.description:
Buttons and Smart Keys  Each button performs a specific action, linking to a file, executing a shell command.
 Explicit Buttons accessible from within a single document;
 Global Buttons accessible anywhere within a user&rsquo;s network of documents;
 Implicit Buttons buttons created and managed by other programs or embedded within the structure of a document, accessible from within a single document. Hyperbole recognizes implicit buttons by contextual patterns given in their type specifications.
